title: Debra Messing / Bronchitis & Head Injury
description: Sean and Dr. Wali talk about travel comfort items. Debra Messing breathes through her story about bronchitis and how she quit smoking. Sean and Debra reminisce about their time on Will & Grace and talk about what it takes to perform on Broadway eight times a week.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
